snippet.title: [Yggdrasil Chronicles - A Tale of Cindrivia] Battle against Chaos The Fallen Angel
snippet.description:
- The Yggdrasil - A Tale of Cindrivia is a NON-PROFIT and FREE TO PLAY project created by Ryan Entertainment Studio (https://www.facebook.com/RyanEntertainmentStudio). We do this with all our passion, not for earning money from it.

"This is a battle against Chaos The Fallen Angel, one of the mighiest bosses."

Engine used: RPG Maker VX Ace
Special thanks to:
- Graphics: Ragnarok Online (Gravity Co. Ltd), Kaduki (http://usui.moo.jp/)
- Battle sound: Final Fantasy VIII - The Extreme (Squaresoft - SquareEnix)
